 "remarks": "Welcome to SONO Place! This stylish 1-bedroom condo offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and flexibility, featuring a dedicated garage parking space plus a bonus loft area ideal for a home office, guest space, or potential second bedroom. The bright and airy living/dining area boasts soaring 13-foot ceilings and oversized windows that fill the space with natural light. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a natural gas range. A generously sized bedroom offers ample closet space, while the full bathroom includes both a tub and shower. Additional features include hardwood floors throughout, central air conditioning, natural gas heat, and an in-unit washer/dryer combo. Water is included in the rent. Pet-friendly for cats and small to medium-sized dogs. The building offers secure elevator access and on-site guest parking. Ideally located in the heart of South Norwalk, you&apos;ll be just steps from the train station, restaurants, shopping, parks, The SoNo Collection, and everything this vibrant neighborhood has to offer. Available July 20th.",
